<xref rid="Tab1" ref-type="table">1</xref> for the validation sample, CFA of the 21-item AHP-SF showed that all indices of model fit met the established criteria. Although the validation sample showed a slightly worse model fit than the calibration sample, the sizes of the factor loadings were similar for the two samples (Table&#x000a0;
